name: Alma
description: A radiant golden straw hue, with a robust all-malt foundation. A refreshing crispness is complemented by delicate floral and citrus notes that emerge in the finish.

name: Array
description: Refreshing Grapefruit and Pineapple. Subtle aroma of lemon.

name: Brahms
description: A gentle roast that harmonizes with a medium-bodied crispness. Delicately balanced by a mild herbal bitterness.

name: Bresa
description: Tart ale with notes of lemon, lime, sea salt and coriander

name: Carnyx
description: Balanced richness, notes of coffee, and chocolate. A smooth, and creamy texture.

name: Dom
description: Crisp ale with floral and pear notes, subtle grapefruit zest aroma.

name: Elias
description: Refreshing and malt forward, subtle citrus notes and floral aroma. Naturally Carbonated.

name: Flux
description: Tropical flavors of bubble gum, pithy orange, papaya, blueberry, and dank citrus. Complex aromas of cannabis, grapefruit, stonefruit, and orange zest. Hops: Columbus, Simcoe, Mosaic, Ekuanot, Comet, Strata.

name: Glyphs
description: Notes of tangerine, orange zest, and aromatic pine. Light bitterness.

name: Kimik
description: An easy drinking ale with heavy punch. With notes of heavy citrus, passion fruit, lychee, and a distinct guava aroma.

name: Lupula
description: Ripe pineapple, mango, and ruby red grapefruit. Very aromatic.

name: Marty
description: Light Matcha-steeped, crisp ale.

name: Melrose
description: Smooth and malty with light caramel and dark fruit notes with subtle cherry aroma.

name: Narada
description: Orange hued with dank citrus and pine notes. Hopped with Citra, Amarillo, Simcoe, Columbus and Michigan Chinook.

name: Pomona
description: Tart ale fruited with cherry and raspberry.

name: Pomona
description: Tart ale fruited with mango and peach.

name: Revive
description: Modern, hopped version of a traditional Finnish fermented-water beverage.

name: Scylla
description: Dark chocolate and toasted caramel layered on a blackberry cola.

name: Sebastian
description: Refreshing and smooth with a kick. A Maibock brewed with 100% Pilsner malt and German and American Noble Hops.

name: Secrets
description: Passionfruit, pine, apricot, and orange zest. Dank pine and blueberry aroma.

name: Soleil
description: Dry orange, mimosa-esque. Floral notes and funky.

name: Terrini
description: Grassy, floral, and pithy orange aromas. Notes of pear, candied orange, and lemongrass flavors. Slightly sweet finish.

name: Tides
description: Cantaloupe with blueberry undertones, earthy and dry passionfruit. Cantaloupe and orange aroma.

name: Waves
description: Undertones of stonefruit and citrus, juicy hop finish. Blueberry and melon aroma. Hops: Columbus, El Dorado, Ekuanot, Citra, Mosaic, Simcoe. Naturally carbonated.
